NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::GenBashCompleter - Create bash completer script for
    your scripts using App::GenBashCompleter

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::GenBashCompleter (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-GenBashCompleter), released on 2014-11-14.

SYNOPSIS
    In "dist.ini":

     [GenBashCompleter]

    After build, if there are any of your scripts (e.g. "bin/foo") which
    App::GenBashCompleter can generate bash completer script for, it will be
    generated (e.g. "bin/_foo") and added to your build.

DESCRIPTION
SEE ALSO
    App::GenBashCompleter

